"Warlock Eldritch Invocation: Otherworldly Leap":
  title: "Warlock Eldritch Invocation Option: Otherworldly Leap"
  desc: "_Prerequisite: Level 2+ Warlock_\n\nYou can cast _Jump_ on yourself without expending a spell slot."
  fields:
  - body: "[Packet 7](https://www.dndbeyond.com/sources/ua/ph-playtest-7)"

"Warlock Eldritch Invocation: Pact of the Blade":
  title: "Warlock Eldritch Invocation Option: Pact of the Blade"
  desc: "_Prerequisite: None_\n\nAs a Bonus Action, you can trace arcane sigils in the air to conjure a pact weapon in your hand—a Simple or Martial melee weapon of your choice with which you bond—or create a bond with a magic weapon you touch. Until the bond ends, you have proficiency with the weapon, you can use its Mastery property, and you can use it as a spellcasting focus.\n\nWhenever you attack with the bonded weapon, you can use your Charisma modifier for the attack and damage rolls, instead of using Strength or Dexterity, and you can cause the weapon to deal Necrotic, Psychic, or Radiant damage or its normal damage type.\n\nYour bond with the weapon ends if you use this feature's Bonus Action again, if the weapon is more than 5 feet away from you for 1 minute or more, or if you die. A conjured weapon disappears when the bond ends."
  fields:
  - body: "[Packet 7](https://www.dndbeyond.com/sources/ua/ph-playtest-7)"

"Warlock Eldritch Invocation: Pact of the Chain":
  title: "Warlock Eldritch Invocation Option: Pact of the Chain"
  desc: "_Prerequisite: Level 2+ Warlock_\n\nYou learn the _Find Familiar_ spell and can cast it as an action without expending a spell slot. When you cast the spell, you choose one of the normal forms for your familiar or one of the following special forms: imp, pseudodragon, quasit, skeleton, slaad tadpole, or sprite.\n\nAdditionally, when you take the Attack action, you can forgo one of your own attacks to allow your familiar to make one attack of its own with its Reaction."
  fields:
  - body: "[Packet 7](https://www.dndbeyond.com/sources/ua/ph-playtest-7)"

"Warlock Eldritch Invocation: Pact of the Tome":
  title: "Warlock Eldritch Invocation Option: Pact of the Tome"
  desc: "_Prerequisite: None_\n\nStitching together strands of shadow, you conjure forth a book in your hand at the end of a Short Rest or Long Rest. This Book of Shadows (you determine its appearance) contains eldritch magic that only you can access, granting you the following benefits:\n\n**Cantrips and Rituals**. When the book appears, choose three cantrips, and choose two level 1 spells that have the Ritual tag. The spells can be from any class's spell list, and they must be spells you don't already have prepared. While the book is on your person, you have the chosen spells prepared, and they function as Warlock spells for you.\n\n**Spell Slot**. You gain a level 1 spell slot. Once you expend it, you can't gain another slot from this feature until you finish a Long Rest.\n\n**Spellcasting Focus**. You can use the book as a Spellcasting Focus.\n\nThe book disappears if you conjure another book with this feature or if you die."
  fields:
  - body: "[Packet 7](https://www.dndbeyond.com/sources/ua/ph-playtest-7)"

"Warlock Eldritch Invocation: Repelling Blast":
  title: "Warlock Eldritch Invocation Option: Repelling Blast"
  desc: "_Prerequisite: Eldritch Blast Cantrip_\n\nWhen you hit a Large or smaller creature with _Eldritch Blast_, you can push that creature up to 10 feet straight away from you."
  fields:
  - body: "[Packet 7](https://www.dndbeyond.com/sources/ua/ph-playtest-7)"

"Warlock Eldritch Invocation: Thirsting Blade":
  title: "Warlock Eldritch Invocation Option: Thirsting Blade"
  desc: "_Prerequisite: Level 5+ Warlock, Pact of the Blade_\n\nYou gain the Extra Attack feature for your pact weapon only. With that feature, you can attack twice with the weapon, instead of once, when you take the Attack action on your turn.\n\nWhen you reach level 11 in this class, this Extra Attack confers two extra attacks rather than one."
  fields:
  - body: "[Packet 7](https://www.dndbeyond.com/sources/ua/ph-playtest-7)"

"Warlock Eldritch Invocation: Visions of Distant Realms":
  title: "Warlock Eldritch Invocation Option: Visions of Distant Realms"
  desc: "_Prerequisite: Level 9+ Warlock_\n\nYou can cast _Arcane Eye_ without expending a spell slot."
  fields:
  - body: "[Packet 7](https://www.dndbeyond.com/sources/ua/ph-playtest-7)"

"Warlock Eldritch Invocation: Whispers of the Grave":
  title: "Warlock Eldritch Invocation Option: Whispers of the Grave"
  desc: "_Prerequisite: Level 7+ Warlock_\n\nYou can cast _Speak with Dead_ without expending a spell slot."
  fields:
  - body: "[Packet 7](https://www.dndbeyond.com/sources/ua/ph-playtest-7)"

"Warlock Eldritch Invocation: Witch Sight":
